name: Ad Infinitum
description:
I am the gray ocean waves
that continue to lap,
as the cool solemn winds
make peace with my soul.
 
A disposable component
of clockwork,
turning for what seems
like eternity.
 
Each day brings us closer to death.
Dreams diluted by
systemic mundanity.
 
Trapped in this madness,
I can only insist on playing a part,
reluctant to show any signs of weakness.
 
And I’ve come to realization
just for my heart to syncopate
to the hums of distraction
 
once more.
